    "body" : "<p>In Android Studio with Kotlin.</p>\n<p>File &gt; Settings,</p>\n<p>Editor &gt; Code Style &gt; Kotlin, then &quot;Imports&quot; tab, select &quot;Use single name import&quot;.</p>\n<p>Also remove <code>import java.util.*</code>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/eBT1d.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/eBT1d.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
