    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1967946,
      "reputation" : 181,
      "user_id" : 1767676,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/a70MG.png?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Karmakulov Kirill",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1767676/karmakulov-kirill"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1751515359,
    "last_edit_date" : 1751515359,
    "creation_date" : 1751515045,
    "answer_id" : 79688284,
    "question_id" : 3348816,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Settings in <code>.editorconfig</code> file in project/module root take precedence over the global settings described in <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/3348855/1767676\">the most voted answer here</a>. So just add (change) there, for Kotlin:</p>\n<pre><code>[*.{kt, kts}]\nij_kotlin_name_count_to_use_star_import = 999\nij_kotlin_name_count_to_use_star_import_for_members = 999\n</code></pre>\n<p>Or, for Java:</p>\n<pre><code>[*.java]\nij_java_names_count_to_use_import_on_demand = 999\nij_java_class_count_to_use_import_on_demand = 999\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
